      • UCSBSection

        public UCSBSection(UCSBLecture parent,
                   String status,
                   String enrollCode,
                   String sectionDay,
                   String sectionTime,
                   String sectionRoom,
                   int enrolled,
                   int capacity)
        Detailed Constructor
        Parameters:
        parent - UCSB lecture object
        status - string object of the status of a class e.g. "Full"
        enrollCode - string object of the enroll code of a class e.g. "07989"
        sectionDay - string object of the days where section is held e.g. "T R"
        sectionTime - string object of the times when section is held e.g. "3:30pm - 4:45pm"
        sectionRoom - string object of the room where section is held e.g. Chem 1171"
        enrolled - integer object of the number of students that are enrolled in the class e.g. from 63/88 take the 63
        capacity - integer object of the amount of students that can enroll in the class e.g. from 63/88 take the 88
